asset.author: Under Armour

transcripts: ua headphones wireless engineered by JBL may look bigger than your standard earbuds their unique design fits into the bowl of your ear vs your inner here this ensures you get a secure fit and never have to worry about the headphones falling out even during the most extreme workouts. These headphones come with two different sized enhances the smaller enhancers size five are pre fit on the headphones, and the larger ones size seven are in the box insert each tip directly into your ear canal a slight twist of the headphones toward your jaw will lock them into place. the correct size will fully fill the bowl of your ear and fits snugly against the edge feeling secure having the right size will not only ensure the best of it but also optimal sound quality. For best overall performance it's recommended to wear the headphones with the cord in front if you choose to wear the cord in the back extensions included to improve stability and keep the cord off your neck. If your headphones become loose you may need the size 7 enhanciers which can be found in the box to change sizes remove the original enhancers then align the sound tunnels of the alternate enhancers and stretch down the edges if you still feel like you don't have the perfect fit our customer care team can help fit you or provide larger or in between sizes.
